videos.headline: Arizona's Tate throws dime into end zone to take the lead
videos.description: Arizona QB Khalil Tate connects with WR Tony Ellison to take a 10-7 lead in first half.

videos.headline: BYU WR makes tip-drill catch to set up TD on next play
videos.description: BYU WR Dylan Collie makes a tip-drill catch to set up a 24-yard touchdown on the next play to put them ahead 14-10.
